reviewText: Hysterical!  Love it!  Shipped timely.  Great transaction overall!

I thought the video was great, funny, and worth the price. But, what I didn't expect was for the game show part of it all. I thought it was going to be another Ralphie stand up. Plus it has a gritty street feel. Like it's an underground video or something. The video came in a plastic case and was well protected. And arrived within the projected delivery window. I would buy again from this seller, if the opportunity arose.
this and all of his videos you need to see and get, i have them all and they will make you laugh your a-- off!
sorry to say this is not what I had hoped it would be.  Ralphie is normally hysterical but this is just stupid.

When I bought this DVD, I was thinking that it was another Ralphie May stand up comedy.  I was wrong, Ralphie May is the host and there are contenders that face one another in a ragging battle.  Who can insult the most or the best.  It was funny, some were just down right sad to listen to.
Shipping was very fast. Not quite what I though tit would be but still funny. Pricing was very good.
Unfortunately, this is one of the lamest things I have ever seen.  It doesn't even deserve 1 star.  All this movie is, is a bunch of people trading stupid insults back and forth....sigh
